    "While it is clear that the unexpected loss leads to a drop in accuracy, we can also expect that the effect of RNA is to make the model more robust to such a modality drop than the \"Source Only\" model, since the latter is less able to exploit the synergies between modalities and, thus, more vulnerable to dominant modalities.",
